obfuscation: I 'll understand , surely !
original: I'll see, surely!

obfuscation: I 'll see myself and Anna married this day , I 'm telling you !
original:
I'll see myself and
Anna married this day, I'm telling you!

obfuscation: It 's quare fool 's blather you have about the sea done this and the sea done that .
original:
It's quare fool's blather you have about the sea done
this and the sea done that.

obfuscation: You 'd ought to be shamed to be saying the alike , and you an old sailor yourself .
original:
You'd ought to be shamed to be saying the
like, and you an old sailor yourself.

obfuscation: I 'm after hearing a lot of it from you and a lot more that Anna 's told me you make be saying to her , and I 'm thinking it 's a poor weak thing you are , and not a man at all !
You see if Ay 'm man -- maybe quicker'n you tank .
original: You see if Ay'm man--maybe quicker'n you tank.

obfuscation: Yerra , make n't be boasting .
original: Yerra, don't be boasting.

obfuscation: I 'm thinking 't is out of your wits you 've got with fright of the sea .
original:
I'm thinking 'tis
out of your wits you've got with fright of the sea.

obfuscation: You 'd be wishing Anna married to a farmer , she told me .
original:
You'd be wishing
Anna married to a farmer, she told me.

obfuscation: That 'd constitute a swate match , surely !
original: That'd be a swate match, surely!

obfuscation: Would you have a fine girl the like of Anna lying down at nights with a muddy scut stinking of pigs and dung ?
original:
Would you have a fine girl the like of Anna lying down at nights with a
muddy scut stinking of pigs and dung?

obfuscation: Or would you have her tied for life to the like of them skinny , shrivelled swabs does exist working in cities ?
original:
Or would you have her tied for
life to the like of them skinny, shrivelled swabs does be working in
cities?

obfuscation: Dat 's lie , you fool !
original: Dat's lie, you fool!

obfuscation: 'Tis not .
original: 'Tis not.

obfuscation: 'T is your own mad notions I 'm after telling .
original: 'Tis your own mad notions I'm after telling.

obfuscation: But you know the truth in your heart , if great fear of the sea has made you a liar and coward itself .
original:
But you
know the truth in your heart, if great fear of the sea has made you a
liar and coward itself.

obfuscation: The sea 's the alone life for a man with guts in him is n't afraid of his own shadow !
original:
The sea's the only life
for a man with guts in him isn't afraid of his own shadow!

obfuscation: 'T is entirely on the sea he 's free , and him roving the face of the world , seeing all things , and not giving a damn for saving up money , or stealing from his friends , or any of the black tricks that a landlubber 'd waste his life on .
original:
'Tis only on
the sea he's free, and him roving the face of the world, seeing all
things, and not giving a damn for saving up money, or stealing from his
friends, or any of the black tricks that a landlubber'd waste his life
on.

obfuscation: 'T was yourself knew it once , and you a bo'sun for years .
original: 'Twas yourself knew it once, and you a bo'sun for years.

obfuscation: You vas crazy fool , Ay tal you !
original: You vas crazy fool, Ay tal you!

obfuscation: You 've swallowed the anchor .
original: You've swallowed the anchor.

obfuscation: The sea give you a clout once knocked you down , and you 're not man enough to get up for another , but lie there for the rest of your life howling bloody murder .
original:
The sea give you a clout once
knocked you down, and you're not man enough to get up for another, but
lie there for the rest of your life howling bloody murder.

obfuscation: Is n't it myself the sea has nearly drowned , and me battered and bate till I was that close to hell I could hear the flames roaring , and never a groan out of me till the sea gave up and it seeing the great strength and guts of a man was in me ?
original:
Isn't it myself the sea has nearly drowned, and me battered and bate
till I was that close to hell I could hear the flames roaring, and
never a groan out of me till the sea gave up and it seeing the great
strength and guts of a man was in me?

obfuscation: Yes , you vas hell of fallar , hear you tal it !
original: Yes, you vas hell of fallar, hear you tal it!

obfuscation: You 'll be calling me a liar once too often , me erstwhile bucko !
original:
You'll be calling me a liar once too often, me old
bucko!

obfuscation: Was n't the unharmed story of it and my picture itself in the newspapers of Boston a week back ?
original:
Wasn't the whole story of it and my picture itself in the
newspapers of Boston a week back?

obfuscation: Sure I 'd like to see you in the best of your youth make the like of what I done in the storm and after .
original:
Sure I'd like to see you in the best of your youth do
the like of what I done in the storm and after.

obfuscation: 'T is a mad lunatic , screeching with fear , you 'd be this minute !
original:
'Tis a mad lunatic,
screeching with fear, you'd be this minute!

obfuscation: Ho-ho !
original: Ho-ho!

obfuscation: You vas young fool !
original: You vas young fool!

obfuscation: In ole years when Ay was on windyammer , Ay vas through hundred storms vorse'n dat !
original:
In ole years when Ay was on
windyammer, Ay vas through hundred storms vorse'n dat!

obfuscation: Ships vas ships den -- and men dat sail on dem vas real men .
original:
Ships vas ships
den--and men dat sail on dem vas real men.

obfuscation: And now what you gat on steamers ?
original:
And now what you gat on
steamers?

obfuscation: You gat fallars on deck make n't know ship from mudscow .
original: You gat fallars on deck don't know ship from mudscow.

obfuscation: And below deck you gat fallars yust know how for shovel coal -- might yust as veil vork on coal vagon ashore !
original:
And below deck you gat fallars yust know how
for shovel coal--might yust as veil vork on coal vagon ashore!

obfuscation: Is it casting insults at the men in the stokehole ye are , ye erstwhile ape ?
original:
Is it casting insults at the men in the
stokehole ye are, ye old ape?

obfuscation: God stiffen you !
original: God stiffen you!

obfuscation: Wan of them is worth any ten stock-fish-swilling Square-heads ever shipped on a windbag !
original:
Wan of them is worth any
ten stock-fish-swilling Square-heads ever shipped on a windbag!
